+  // re-rasterizes a dynamic glyph texture EVERY frame, so its pages are invalidated every frame
+  // and hit this race -> vertical-striped glyphs that vary per render. The global lock is a
+  // recursive std::mutex; acquiring it here once per frame is cheap. See KB 65.
+  auto global_lock = global_critical_region_.Acquire();
